<head>LIGHTNING</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">閃電 </item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>The WEATHER condition constituted by flashes of lightning.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The standard word for lightning is diàn 電.</p>
        </div>
