<p>LIGHTNING</p>
<p>fulgur refers to the momentary shining of lightning on the horizon in single flashes.</p>
<p>fulguratio refers to the continued shining of lightning, or the repeated flashes of lightning.</p>
<p>fulmen refers to the lightning that strikes the earth and might strike a person, like Greek keraunos.</p>
